dcterms:description: The mini ImageNet dataset is a standard benchmark for few-shot image classification, consisting of 100 randomly chosen classes from ILSVRC-2012, with each class containing 600 images of size 84 × 84.
dcterms:title: miniImageNet

dcterms:description: The FC100 dataset is constructed from the CIFAR-100 dataset, containing 100 classes grouped into 20 super-classes, with each class containing 600 images of size 32 × 32.
dcterms:title: FC100
